title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 66] Rock, Pop-Rock, New Wave-Rock
description:
I was supposed to be off the radar for a while, but I guess it was not meant to be! Here are four other good records from the best decade of music. Paris Black and Taxxi are more obscure than the other two and ultra rare to grab. They will surely be a great listening experience for those who like synthpop (Paris Black) and new wave/Rock (Taxxi). I love the track "I'm No Angel". Taxxi should have been/could have been big, but I assume it was not meant to be either! finally you know what to do after downloading....seed people!
